name: depfinder
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "depfinder" %}
{% set version = "2.9.1" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/depfinder-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 6b058dadbfc9970e7a6bf36ba0c9357cf4c14a926b5b4644f3ea192e6649cd8a

build:
  entry_points:
    - depfinder = depfinder.cli:cli
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv
  number: 0
  skip: true  # [py>310]

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - python
    - pyyaml
    - requests
    - stdlib-list  # [py<310]

test:
  imports:
    - depfinder
  commands:
    - pip check
    - depfinder --help
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: http://github.com/ericdill/depfinder
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Find all the unique imports in your library

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ericdill
    - mariusvniekerk
    - tonyfast
    - ocefpaf
    - CJ-Wright
    - beckermr
